Class UIAutomatorTestIntroScreensActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • pylapp.smoothclicker.android.AbstractTest
      • pylapp.smoothclicker.android.uiautomator.UIAutomatorTestIntroScreensActivity

  • public class UIAutomatorTestIntroScreensActivity
extends AbstractTest
    Class to use to make UI tests with UIAutomator of the IntroScreensActivity. Warning: The intro screens activity is displayed only one time, so we should run these tests before all other tests cases

    22/03/2016
    Version:
    1.1.0
    Author:
